---
title: Fajita-Style Veggie Bowls with Beyond Meat®, Basmati Rice and Lime Crema
description: Easy, fast and packed with flavour, this dish gives you the fiesta without the fuss! Bell peppers and green onions pair perfectly with tender Beyond Meat® for a delicious fajita bowl that comes together with smoky Mexican-style seasoning.
